TITLE: Cameron Dicker's clutch kicks lift Chargers to three-point win
SUMMARY: Los Angeles Chargers kicker Cameron Dicker nailed two late field goals to help the team narrowly beat the Atlanta Falcons, 20-17, on Sunday.

TITLE: Bengals' Joe Mixon carries offense with five touchdowns, blows out Panthers at home
SUMMARY: Cincinnati Bengals running back Joe Mixon beat up the Carolina Panthers' defense, scoring five touchdowns to help pick up a 42-21 win on Sunday.

TITLE: New York governor: Lee Zeldin supporter attacked at rally for Gov. Kathy Hochul, video shows
SUMMARY: A female supporter of GOP gubernatorial candidate Lee Zeldin says she was attacked and assaulted at a rally for Democratic Gov. Kathy Hochul in New York City on Saturday.

TITLE: Ex-MLB star Lenny Dykstra pins Phillies' World Series struggles on Jill Biden's appearance
SUMMARY: Jill Biden took in the Philadelphia Phillies' Game 4 loss to the Houston Astros, and Lenny Dykstra said her appearance changed everything.
